# Baselines registry (G4).
#
# Each subdirectory is one baseline configuration:
#   baselines/<task_id>/
#     config.toml          - the SceneBuilder / training inputs
#     expected_metrics.json - target metrics + tolerance
#     manifest.json        - RunManifest captured when the baseline was last recaptured
#
# CI compares fresh runs against these; the `clankers compare` CLI surface
# (G3) renders deltas. Baselines are recaptured manually via the
# workflow_dispatch baseline job; see `.github/workflows/ci.yml`.
